'''Russians in Spain''' form one of the country's smaller foreign communities, making up about 0.83% of all foreigners in Spain.<ref name="INE"/>

==History==
During the [[Spanish Civil War]] there were 72 [[White émigré]] volunteers on the [[Spain under Franco|Nationalist side]], as well as some hundreds of Soviet advisors on the [[Second Spanish Republic|Republican side]].<ref>{{harvnb|Keene|2001|p=188}}</ref><ref>{{harvnb|Alcofar Nassaes|1971}}</ref>
